{"tid":719447,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠片《小偷家族》在日本被右翼狂插: 「日本國恥」","createTime":"2018-06-27T12:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T03:04:26.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c204a733be8f22a5812362b4c1c0e6de6fcfb7d7","tid":719447,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"網頁有劇透, 我只貼無劇透既部分<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://medium.com/%E5%A4%A7%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%86%E7%AB%99/%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E8%A8%8E%E5%8E%AD-%E5%B0%8F%E5%81%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F-d1477b8170c1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%2599%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258F%25B3%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E8%25A8%258E%25E5%258E%25AD-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F-d1477b8170c1&d=KEBMhe5rGA8bf52ZRo792f6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=8187ff9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://medium.com/%E5%A4%A7%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%86%E7%AB%99/%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E8%A8%8E%E5%8E%AD-%E5%B0%8F%E5%81%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F-d1477b8170c1</a></span><br />\n<br />\n大福<br />\nJun 25<br />\n為什麼日本右翼討厭《小偷家族》？<br />\n<br />\n今年康城勇奪金棕櫚大獎的日本電影《小偷家族（万引き家族）》，對不同類型的觀眾來說有不同意義：對是枝裕和導演的忠粉來說，《小偷家族》絕對是「是枝宇宙」的「集大成」之作（雖然導演不這樣認為）；對喜歡追趕話題的一般觀眾來說，《小偷家族》亦是以小人物出發，談論「家庭」與「血緣」的優秀小品電影，拍攝手法平易近人，效果亦是有笑有淚；但對於日本右翼來說，《小偷家族》卻是礙眼的存在。<br />\n<br />\n「日本賣國賊」是枝裕和？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《小偷家族》是繼1997年今村昌平的《鰻魚》之後再奪金棕櫚，但以首相安倍晉三為首的日本政府卻態度冷淡，並沒有立即向是枝裕和祝賀，</strong>與以往安倍晉三立即祝賀的「為國爭光」日本人（如男子花樣滑冰奧運金牌得主羽生結弦、諾貝爾文學獎得主石黑英雄，縱使這位只是英籍日裔&hellip;）不一樣，此現象更被法國媒體大肆報導，反過來引起日本國內注意。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，著名右翼人物紛紛表達對《小偷家族》勇奪金棕櫚的不滿，包括屢起爭議的作家百田尚樹，及美容外科醫學博士高須克彌，均開腔批評指是枝裕和「抹黑日本的形象」、「《小偷家族》的日本人形象令人討厭，日本人明明禮儀周正」，<strong>網路亦有不少右翼留言稱是枝裕和是「賣國賊」，「日本人才不會以偷竊為生」、「電影向外國宣揚日本負面形象」、「教唆偷竊的電影應評為『R』級別（未滿15歲禁止觀賞）」，甚至「《小偷家族》在康城得獎乃日本國恥」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>右翼甚至趁著金棕櫚大獎為是枝裕和挖掘「反日」歷史，像《海街女孩日記》中吃飯時的「立膝」亦被認為是朝鮮式的「粗魯失禮」，不符合日本禮數云云，</strong>加上其後是枝裕和拒絕文部科學省的祝賀邀請，表示身為文化人希望與公權力保持距離，引發更多爭議。縱使《小偷家族》飽受網路右翼的留言攻擊，仍然無礙電影奪得好票房，上映3週已累積25億，為近年日本真人電影罕見的好成績，「爭議＝話題」絕對是票房成功的法則，但身為海外影迷應該會疑惑，究竟《小偷家族》觸及日本右翼哪些禁忌呢？<br />\n.....<br />\n無論是戲裡各種赤貧線下的面貌，或者戲外與「五毛」毫無分別，保守又偏激的鍵盤戰士發言，對一眾對日本有憧憬，視之為「鄉下」的觀眾來說，《小偷家族》絕對是個有意思的震撼教育。"},{"pid":"0cd4d4ea6dcadefae42d609264b8cb2e432e7462","tid":719447,"uid":35870,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？睇完成篇文都唔知套戲大約講乜"},{"pid":"1f08d045fa5974cf38321b4eeecd2b9ab94829c6","tid":719447,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"日本網民留言<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://read01.com/O3K4AM6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FO3K4AM6.html&d=KEBMhe5rGA8bf52ZRo792f6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=49a18229\" target=\"_blank\">http://read01.com/O3K4AM6.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><br />\n是枝裕和擅自代表日本發言。《小偷家族》那篇採訪中滿是反日思想</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/202031_71d5039cf1209140b9105a4696b0b155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F202031_71d5039cf1209140b9105a4696b0b155.jpg&h=f367b99e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>是枝裕和是日本腦殘左派的典型</strong>。對日本毫無主人公意識。比起自己的日本人身份，更在意謎一般的精英意識，更莫名其妙地對日本進行批判。沒有主人公意識的人作品沒有靈魂。明理之人不會為這種虛偽感動到。這種人不可能拍出好作品。他的作品就是胡扯，稱不上名作。所以每回都拿不到獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/202128_8a64ea7a1756fdf5993772ceeace6eb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F202128_8a64ea7a1756fdf5993772ceeace6eb7.jpg&h=3632cd1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a05cd40270e3d6f31c9f448248ca582f02c8c4a","tid":719447,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd4d4ea6dcadefae42d609264b8cb2e432e7462","tid":719447,"uid":35870,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？睇完成篇文都唔知套戲大約講乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"成篇文無穿到電影最重要既twist"},{"pid":"23d623b7d3b89f7d103bc3619738bea852a5cac7","tid":719447,"uid":147345,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"日本有班右翼不嬲都好on9,你search下「万引き家族 ネトウヨ」就知好多人都屌緊佢地"},{"pid":"24e824f634d699660c6f163fb6682480f75862f9","tid":719447,"uid":63950,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3e3fc47ca72d4038a32a0005735418b8fe55555","tid":719447,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"on9架仔，睇到自己咁清高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df33217091e19fe339defb929d30755ef34ee0f","tid":719447,"uid":11185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"是枝反修正歷史得罪右翼，係早十幾年前既事"},{"pid":"b8011e1d99cda31dfbaf54b718dccfe08cce5523","tid":719447,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7df33217091e19fe339defb929d30755ef34ee0f","tid":719447,"uid":11185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"是枝反修正歷史得罪右翼，係早十幾年前既事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:43:39.000Z","msg":"而家日本正係呢班右翼得勢<br />\n<br />\n安倍自己都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f3f0599cd8a765044bdb561fb6e3e1d6926dce","tid":719447,"uid":34965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24e824f634d699660c6f163fb6682480f75862f9","tid":719447,"uid":63950,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T04:04:26.000Z","msg":"無帶個腦去睇？"},{"pid":"cc594b84e2184df342814c8c272ae4c908a69f03","tid":719447,"uid":175997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c204a733be8f22a5812362b4c1c0e6de6fcfb7d7","tid":719447,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"網頁有劇透, 我只貼無劇透既部分<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://medium.com/%E5%A4%A7%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%86%E7%AB%99/%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E8%A8%8E%E5%8E%AD-%E5%B0%8F%E5%81%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F-d1477b8170c1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%2599%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258F%25B3%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E8%25A8%258E%25E5%258E%25AD-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F-d1477b8170c1&d=KEBMhe5rGA8bf52ZRo792f6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=8187ff9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://medium.com/%E5%A4%A7%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%86%E7%AB%99/%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E8%A8%8E%E5%8E%AD-%E5%B0%8F%E5%81%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F-d1477b8170c1</a></span><br />\n<br />\n大福<br />\nJun 25<br />\n為什麼日本右翼討厭《小偷家族》？<br />\n<br />\n今年康城勇奪金棕櫚大獎的日本電影《小偷家族（万引き家族）》，對不同類型的觀眾來說有不同意義：對是枝裕和導演的忠粉來說，《小偷家族》絕對是「是枝宇宙」的「集大成」之作（雖然導演不這樣認為）；對喜歡追趕話題的一般觀眾來說，《小偷家族》亦是以小人物出發，談論「家庭」與「血緣」的優秀小品電影，拍攝手法平易近人，效果亦是有笑有淚；但對於日本右翼來說，《小偷家族》卻是礙眼的存在。<br />\n<br />\n「日本賣國賊」是枝裕和？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《小偷家族》是繼1997年今村昌平的《鰻魚》之後再奪金棕櫚，但以首相安倍晉三為首的日本政府卻態度冷淡，並沒有立即向是枝裕和祝賀，</strong>與以往安倍晉三立即祝賀的「為國爭光」日本人（如男子花樣滑冰奧運金牌得主羽生結弦、諾貝爾文學獎得主石黑英雄，縱使這位只是英籍日裔&hellip;）不一樣，此現象更被法國媒體大肆報導，反過來引起日本國內注意。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，著名右翼人物紛紛表達對《小偷家族》勇奪金棕櫚的不滿，包括屢起爭議的作家百田尚樹，及美容外科醫學博士高須克彌，均開腔批評指是枝裕和「抹黑日本的形象」、「《小偷家族》的日本人形象令人討厭，日本人明明禮儀周正」，<strong>網路亦有不少右翼留言稱是枝裕和是「賣國賊」，「日本人才不會以偷竊為生」、「電影向外國宣揚日本負面形象」、「教唆偷竊的電影應評為『R』級別（未滿15歲禁止觀賞）」，甚至「《小偷家族》在康城得獎乃日本國恥」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>右翼甚至趁著金棕櫚大獎為是枝裕和挖掘「反日」歷史，像《海街女孩日記》中吃飯時的「立膝」亦被認為是朝鮮式的「粗魯失禮」，不符合日本禮數云云，</strong>加上其後是枝裕和拒絕文部科學省的祝賀邀請，表示身為文化人希望與公權力保持距離，引發更多爭議。縱使《小偷家族》飽受網路右翼的留言攻擊，仍然無礙電影奪得好票房，上映3週已累積25億，為近年日本真人電影罕見的好成績，「爭議＝話題」絕對是票房成功的法則，但身為海外影迷應該會疑惑，究竟《小偷家族》觸及日本右翼哪些禁忌呢？<br />\n.....<br />\n無論是戲裡各種赤貧線下的面貌，或者戲外與「五毛」毫無分別，保守又偏激的鍵盤戰士發言，對一眾對日本有憧憬，視之為「鄉下」的觀眾來說，《小偷家族》絕對是個有意思的震撼教育。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"文學奬得主應該係石黑一雄<br />\n石黑英雄最近變咗光之巨人"},{"pid":"06a735d418e0990242bf734b8162c7cd1bf280a2","tid":719447,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d38e643b87389ea8ae5e965e27e534a505111d7","tid":719447,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:14:04.000Z","msg":"右膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548c7a0c4f8227828e9a4a0037f05713390ecd3c","tid":719447,"uid":12991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"有幾震撼呀<br />\n日劇都好多依類題材啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94296436c6dac039e43e0c7c12e3ffd6f8095c38","tid":719447,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f47bc78db1bcf6ce7f130d74000b5b1ac0f524a","tid":719447,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"今日睇左，其中一個大女好大波又做雞"},{"pid":"fef11d7b3c8407403670681b237f8d7ef6066d9d","tid":719447,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"cc台手足支持日本右翼清算左膠"},{"pid":"d79ecb6f0e0434d9e5791bea108e63873848f74e","tid":719447,"uid":65400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24e824f634d699660c6f163fb6682480f75862f9","tid":719447,"uid":63950,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:04:17.000Z","m